  "whatsapp_greeting": "Hey, thanks for reaching out to J. Worden & Sons. I'm your paving consultant \u2014 40+ years of Virginia asphalt knowledge at your fingertips. Tell me about your project (driveway, parking lot, industrial?) and your zip code, and I'll get you specific, no-BS answers. I can even book a site visit straight into our calendar. If you want a human foreman instead, just say \"call me\" and I'll set it up within 24 hours.",
  "telegram_greeting": "Hi \u2014 I'm the J. Worden & Sons paving consultant. Family-owned paving in Central Virginia since 1984. Tell me what you're trying to pave and where, and I'll give you real numbers, real timelines, and real answers \u2014 and can book a site visit on the spot. Say \"call me\" anytime to connect with a live foreman.",
